reviewText: Amazing account of gods irresistible love in drawing us to himself
We had never heard his life story before, it was a difficult early life, but what a joy in the healing that Jesus brought!
Wow, such an inspiration. Have plans to share it with others!
Wonderful story of hardship turned into Hope. Hard to read about the troubles but  the journey makes him who he is. Very inspiring.
Excellent in every respect.  Thank you!!
